    "hc_tab_content_highlights_U6AUr3": {
      "type": "hc-tab-content-highlights",
      "blocks": {
        "sheets_for_men_ihWnyx": {
          "type": "sheets-for-men",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "We created the best towel for men.",
            "subheading": "You shower to get clean.",
            "subheading_line2": "Your towel should keep you that way.",
            "description": "Men sweat more, use their towels harder, and wash them less often than most towel manufacturers ever designed for. That gap is exactly what the Jax Towel was built to fill.",
            "cta_text": "Get to know the technology before you experience the difference.",
            "scroll_target": "self-cleaning",
            "bg_color": "#000000",
            "heading_color": "#ffffff",
            "accent_color": "#b45309",
            "description_color": "#9ca3af"
          }
        },
        "inhospitable_germs_Wmi4zX": {
          "type": "inhospitable-germs",
          "settings": {
            "tag": "01 — Deep-Core Sanitation",
            "heading": "Inhospitable for Germs",
            "description": "<p>While standard towels harbor moisture and bacteria in their loops, the <strong>coconut charcoal viscose</strong> and copper infused cotton blend in the Jax Towel creates an inhospitable environment for germs, keeping every use significantly cleaner and fresher than a conventional towel.</p>",
            "card_title": "MICROBIAL BARRIER ANALYSIS",
            "row1_label": "Staphylococcus",
            "row1_width": "99.9%",
            "row1_label_right": "99.9%",
            "row2_label": "E. Coli",
            "row2_width": "99.7%",
            "row2_label_right": "99.7%",
            "row3_label": "Candida",
            "row3_width": "99.1%",
            "row3_label_right": "99.1%",
            "footer_note": "*Tested under ISO 20743 standards for anti-bacterial activity*",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "min_height": "60vh",
            "html_id": "",
            "enable_section_animation": false,
            "tooltip_trigger": "coconut charcoal viscose",
            "tooltip_content": "<p><strong>WHAT IS COCONUT CHARCOAL VISCOSE?</strong></p><p>Coconut Charcoal Viscose is a fiber made from bamboo pulp blended with activated charcoal derived from coconut shells. The coconut shells are burned at high temperatures to create a highly porous form of carbon, which is then infused into viscose fiber. This process gives the filling a unique microscopic structure — millions of tiny pores that are invisible to the eye but highly active in regulating your sleep environment. It is a natural, sustainably sourced material that brings functional benefits far beyond what conventional fillings can offer.</p><p><strong>WHY IS IT IN THE JAX COMFORTER</strong></p><p>Coconut Charcoal Viscose works as the filling of the JAX Comforter because of how much it does passively while you sleep. Its porous structure absorbs excess moisture and humidity from your body, keeping the inside of the comforter dry and preventing that heavy, damp feeling that disrupts sleep. The activated charcoal also naturally traps and neutralizes odor-causing particles, so the comforter stays fresher for longer without relying on chemical treatments. Beyond that, the fiber helps regulate temperature by absorbing excess heat when you run warm and releasing it when you cool down, reducing the discomfort of overheating through the night. The result is a filling that actively works with your body — keeping you dry, cool, and comfortable from the moment you get in.</p>",
            "tooltip_position": "center",
            "bg_color": "#ffffff",
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "accent_color": "#b45309",
            "desc_color": "#4b5563",
            "card_heading_color": "#9ca3af",
            "card_border_color": "#000000",
            "bar_track_color": "#f3f4f6",
            "bar_fill_color": "#000000"
          }
        },
        "acne_shield_cpnML4": {
          "type": "acne-shield",
          "settings": {
            "tag": "02 — Ion-Infused Recovery",
            "heading": "Skin Clarity Support",
            "description": "<p>Our specialized fiber technology supports skin clarity. By reducing the presence of surface bacteria that causes breakouts, this towel acts as the final step in your skincare routine.</p>",
            "card_title": "MICROBIOME PROTECTION",
            "stat_value": "99.9%",
            "stat_unit": "Kill Rate",
            "stat_title": "Bacteria Neutralization",
            "stat_desc": "Destroys acne-causing microbes every 180 seconds.",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "style_preset": "ion_recovery",
            "html_id": "",
            "enable_section_animation": false,
            "tooltip_trigger": "Silver Grid",
            "tooltip_content": "<p><strong>What is it?</strong></p><p>A silver grid is a network of ultra-fine silver threads woven directly into the fabric at precise intervals, forming a continuous grid structure throughout the textile. Unlike silver ion treatments that are applied to the surface of a fabric and degrade with washing, a woven silver grid is a permanent part of the sheet's construction. It does not wash out, fade, or lose effectiveness over time.</p><p><strong>Why is it in the Jax Sheets?</strong></p><p>Silver is one of the most effective natural antimicrobial elements known, and in the Jax Sheets it works continuously to inhibit the growth of bacteria, fungi, and odor-causing microbes across the entire surface of the fabric. Because the silver is woven in rather than coated on, its protective properties remain consistent wash after wash and year after year. The result is a sheet that maintains a genuinely hygienic sleep surface over the long term, without relying on chemical treatments or needing to be replaced to stay effective.</p>",
            "tooltip_position": "center",
            "bg_color": "#000000",
            "text_color": "#fafafa",
            "accent_color": "#b45309",
            "desc_color": "#4b5563"
          }
        },
        "faster_drying_ecWfnz": {
          "type": "faster-drying",
          "settings": {
            "tag": "03 — Zero-Damp Technology",
            "heading": "2x Faster Drying",
            "description": "<p>Because air flows through the hexagonal channels of the weave, the towel dries 2x faster than traditional towels, preventing that \"sour towel\" smell common in humid bathrooms.</p>",
            "visual_title": "Active Ventilation",
            "visual_subtitle": "Means 2 Times Faster Drying",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "min_height": "60vh",
            "html_id": "",
            "enable_section_animation": false,
            "bg_color": "#ffffff",
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "accent_color": "#b45309",
